</div>
</p>
<p>This is totally optional, but has a bunch of benefits. First, if you pass
something else in, you'll get a much clearer error message. Second, it
documents the class even further. A developer now knows exactly what methods
she can call on these objects. And third, if you use an IDE, this gives you
auto-completion! Type-hinting is optional, but I highly recommend it.</p>
<h2 id="adding-an-interface">Adding an Interface <a class="headerlink" href="injection-interfaces#adding-an-interface" title="Permalink to this headline"><i class="fa fa-link" aria-hidden="true"></i></a></h2>
<p>Right now we're injecting an <code>SmtpMailer</code>. But in reality, <code>FriendHarvester</code>
only cares that the mailer has a <code>sendMessage()</code> method on it. But even if we 
had another class with an identical method, like <code>SendMailMailer</code>, for example, 
we couldn't use it because of the specific type-hint.</p>
<p>To make this more awesome, create a new <code>MailerInterface.php</code> file, which holds
an interface with the single send method that all mailers must have:</p>
<p><div class="code-block-wrapper" data-code-block-guid="76c4fbea25">
    <div class="meta">
        <div class="actions">
            <span class="fa fa-clipboard js-activate-clipboard" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Copy Code" data-placement="top"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="info">
                        <span class="js-expand-all" data-range="1-8" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show All Lines" data-placement="top">
                <i class="fa fa-expand js-icon-load-more"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </span>
            
            8 lines <span class="meta-divider"></span> <span title="src/DiDemo/Mailer/MailerInterface.php">src/DiDemo/Mailer/MailerInterface.php</span>
        </div>
    </div>
    <table class="hljs code-block-table">
        <tbody class="js-tr-container">
                <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-expandable" data-range="1-2" data-last="0">
                <i class="fa fa-arrows-v js-icon-load-more" data-toggle="tooltip" title="Show Lines" data-placement="left"></i>
                <i class="fa fa-spinner fa-spin js-icon-loading"></i>
            </td>
            <td class="gap-line">
                                                    ... lines 1 - 2
                            </td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
                    <td class="line-number line-number-displayed" data-line-number-displayed="3"></td>
            <td class="blob-code"><span class="hljs-keyword">namespace</span> <span class="hljs-title">DiDemo</span>\<span class="hljs-title">Mailer</span>;</td>
            </tr>
    <tr>
